run with the following:

ON FIRST RUN
ansible-galaxy install -p ./roles/ -r requirements.yml
ansible-playbook pip.yml
ansible-playbook prov.yml -e "mysql_root='_secure_pass_' mysql_host='_server_hostname_'"

then, later:

ansible-playbook add.yml -e "wp_email=postmaster@_domain_ wp_host=_wordpress_url_ wp_pass=_cli_pass_ wp_account=_cli_user_"

then, pull over the old db and wp-content files from wherever they are. (if you are migrating)
